  "description": "<p><strong>科大讯飞今日正式发布输入法PC版。讯飞输入法PC版是集成了语音、手写、拼音输入，以语音识别能力和触摸板手写输入为特色。</strong>讯飞输入法PC版根据具体的使用环境设置了安静和嘈杂两种语音输入模式，默认视为嘈杂模式。般在嘈杂的环境中，用户每说完一句话后，讯飞输入法都会暂时停止录音，这个时候需要点击一下鼠标，才能说下一句。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e71c3ca/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244162.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%AF%E9%A3%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95PC%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244162.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%AF%E9%A3%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95PC%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244162.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%AF%E9%A3%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95PC%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244162.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%AF%E9%A3%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95PC%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244162.htm&amp;t=%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%AF%E9%A3%9E%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%8F%91%E5%B8%83%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E6%B3%95PC%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal